        android:layout_height="76dp"
        android:clickable="false"
        android:fontFamily="@font/radley"
        android:gravity="left"
        android:text="How to first get to know someone!\n
        Includes: \n
        • How to introduce yourself. \n
        • Things to look out for when talking to your friend. \n
        • Information you should share about yourself. \n
        • How to keep in touch with friends outside of school."
